	</a>
	<a class="share-twitter" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.welivesecurity.com%2F2017%2F12%2F20%2Fadventures-cybersecurity-risk%2F&text=Adventures in cybersecurity research: Risk, cultural theory, and the white male effect &#8211; part 2%0A&via=welivesecurity" target="blank" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" data-original-title="Share on Twitter">
		<span class="icomoon icon-icon_tw"></span>
